node.text:
The insane Bugatti Bolide x The New @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron TourBillon Baguette White Diamonds 💎 

This @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Baguette Rose Gold showcases over 17.80 carats of baguette diamonds along with blue sapphires covering the this high jewelry masterpiece. It features a fully fully working replica of the Bugatti “W16" engine, there's a 30 degree inclined 60-second flying tourbillon visible through a replica of the horseshoe- shaped Bugatti grille.

What do you think? 🔥 #jacobandco
